AndThe Winners Are:
[INLINE] Editor'sChoice for "Best Buy: Power User's PC," is a tie between two
speed demons inthis survey: the Dell XPS P120c and the Comtex Mach 5 P55CMS. 

   For under $4,000, (confirmed by quotes from Toronto area retailers),
   theDell XPS P120c unit combined extremely high-speed with
   excellentengineering, first-rate components and high overall quality.
   The price includedan extended warranty coverage, to supplement the
   regular one-year onsite Dellwarranty with a limited additional two
